    title: "Figma vs Canva for Teams in 2026: Which Design Tool Is Right for Your Organization?",
    date: "Apr 3, 2026",
    excerpt: "Figma and Canva serve very different teams. Here's how to decide which design tool your organization actually needs in 2026.",
